cloudy; Macon 53 foggy; Miami 76 fair; New York 55 fair;
Philadelphia 49 foggy; Pittsburgh 52 fair; Portland, Maine 34 fair;
Richmond 60 fair; Tampa 63 fair; Washington, D.C. 52 fair.
   _Central: Birmingham 66 rain; Bismarck 24 snow; Chicago 60
partly cloudy; Denver 32 partly cloudy; Des Moines 35 fair; Fort
Worth 66; Indianapolis 58 partly cloudy; Kansas City 52 partly
cloudy; Little Rock 70 cloudy; Louisville 62 cloudy; Memphis 67
cloudy; Nashville 65 cloudy; New Orleans 72 cloudy; North Platte 24
fair; Oklahoma City 62 fair; Omaha 30 fair; Rapid City 23 cloudy;
St. Louis 66 partly cloudy; Minneapolis-St. Paul 30 partly cloudy;
Sault Ste. Marie 38 cloudy; San Antonio 71 foggy.
   _West: Albuquerque 41 fair; Anchorage 01 fair; Boise 39 partly
cloudy; Casper 33 cloudy; Fairbanks 09 snow; Great Falls 30 fair;
Honolulu 75 fair; Las Vegas 51 fair; Los Angeles 59 hazy; Medford
40 partly cloudy; Pendleton 43 windy; Phoenix 60 fair; Portland,
Ore. 43 partly cloudy; Reno 37 fair; Salt Lake City 42 fair; San
Diego 61 cloudy; San Francisco 51 partly cloudy; Seattle 44 partly
cloudy; Spokane 33 windy.
   _International: Calgary 32 partly cloudy; Montreal 32 rain;
Ottawa 32 rain; Regina 25 cloudy; Toronto 59 partly cloudy;
Acapulco 79 partly cloudy.
