and Cuba, and Culture Minister Jorge Semprun, Berga said.
   Ibarruri's body was to lie in state until Thursday, when party
leaders have scheduled a commemorative rally in downtown Madrid.
Burial is scheduled later that day at a municipal cemetery beside
the tomb of Spanish Socialist Party founder Pablo Iglesias.
